item.title: [HBASE-16092] Procedure v2 - complete child procedure support
item.description:
There was a missing part on the child procedure tracking.
child procedure were never deleted from the wal on parent completion,
leading to failures on startup. (no code uses child procedures yet)
item.summary: Procedure v2 - complete child procedure support

status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.
